<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-purple);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Commercial Fit-out</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Category A Fit-out</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Category A fit-out across London and the South East — the landlord works that turn a bare shell into a clean, lettable floor. Raised floors, suspended ceilings, base M&amp;E and finishes, delivered to a spec that lets straight away, with the M&amp;E held in-house rather than sub-let.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Category A Fit-out →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Category A Fit-out,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Raised access floors &amp; suspended ceilings</li><li>Base-build M&amp;E — mechanical, electrical &amp; public health</li><li>Lighting, small power &amp; containment to a lettable standard</li><li>Wall, floor &amp; ceiling finishes to landlord spec</li><li>Toilet cores, lift lobbies &amp; common parts</li><li>Landlord works &amp; shell upgrades ahead of letting</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li><li>Building Regulations Part B — fire safety</li><li>Building Regulations Part M — access, and Part L — energy</li><li>BS 8000 — workmanship on building sites</li><li>BCO Guide to Specification — the Cat A benchmark</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>What's included in a Category A fit-out?</summary><p>Category A is the landlord's base finish: raised access floors, suspended ceilings, base M&amp;E, lighting and finishes to a blank, lettable shell. It gives an incoming tenant a clean, code-compliant floor to fit out from. We also handle toilet cores, lift lobbies and common-part upgrades where the let needs them.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Where does Cat A stop and Cat B begin?</summary><p>Cat A is the landlord's responsibility — the lettable base. Cat B is the occupier fit-out on top: partitions, joinery, meeting rooms and FF&amp;E. We deliver both, so the handover between landlord works and tenant fit-out doesn't fall between two contractors.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you deliver the M&amp;E within the Cat A, or sub-let it?</summary><p>We hold the M&amp;E in-house. The base mechanical, electrical and public-health package is delivered by the same contractor as the fabric, coordinated under one programme — which removes the most common source of programme slip on a Cat A floor.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Commercial Fit-out</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/commercial/">Commercial Fit-out overview</a><a class="sector" href="/commercial/cat-b/">Category B Fit-out</a><a class="sector" href="/commercial/refurbishment/">Refurbishment</a><a class="sector" href="/commercial/integrated-me/">Integrated M&amp;E</a></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">The other three lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Groundworks</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme and stage if you can.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Enquire about MEPH →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/compliance/">Compl